{"tid":1614362,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"教大嘅同學你地訓撚醒未啊？","createTime":"2019-10-02T18:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T18:47:09.000Z","uid":176973,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"12230a6182c6a3ceea9e71d70b6b862b9e65ea1a","tid":1614362,"uid":176973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vi58ug6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvi58ug6.jpg&h=bb968f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文宣只可以痴B1-B4 G/F?<br />\n個範圍咁細你痴到幾多啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教大同學真係好循規蹈矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連痴文宣都要得到校方同意<br />\n有同學犧牲 有同學被捕<br />\n校方有冇出嚟譴責過呢個政府同警察？<br />\n校方有冇出嚟保護過同學？<br />\n仲叫我哋珍惜愛護教大呢個家盡量唔好用噴膠<br />\n點解要接受佢哋開出嚟嘅條件？<br />\n點解要向校方妥協？<br />\n校方係維穩嘅工具 服從政府<br />\n你向校方妥協即係向政府妥協<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人再無退路</span></span><br />\n表達訴求係人權同學術自由<br />\n向校方妥協簡直不知所謂<br />\n如果你因為死物而放棄言論自由<br />\n你同淨係關心閘機 罔顧人命嘅林鄭月娥有咩分別？<br />\n我哋要貫徹撕一貼十嘅精神<br />\n教大同學 我哋冇得再咁懦弱<br />\n因為香港人真係輸唔起.....<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">NOW OR NEVER</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n如果張仁良出嚟譴責政府<br />\n係政府回應五大訴求後<br />\n我哋會親手清理翻所有親手痴嘅文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n香港人加油</span>"},{"pid":"7ee1b2f22a958c12fa875890c7d2b5f05df93d35","tid":1614362,"uid":324085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12230a6182c6a3ceea9e71d70b6b862b9e65ea1a","tid":1614362,"uid":176973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vi58ug6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvi58ug6.jpg&h=bb968f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文宣只可以痴B1-B